<config>
	<para_date date="10月23日" week="星期四" weather="晴">
	<para_msg paragraph="10289900" start_scence_sound="950004.mp3">
			<content effect_num="0" />
	</para_msg>	
	<para_msg paragraph="10290000" >
			<content effect_num="2" >又是这样……因为白天睡得太久，晚上无论如何都没有睡意。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10290100" >
			<content effect_num="0" >几乎整个晚上我都在思考“如何才能不给音姐添那么多麻烦”的问题，直到天快亮了才勉强睡着。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10290200" next_p="10328200">
			<content effect_num="0" >于是理所当然的，再次醒过来之后……</content>
	</para_msg>		
	<para_msg paragraph="10328200" >
			<content effect_num="2" talker="李俊明">……干……</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10328300" >
			<content effect_num="0" >闹钟的时针已经游走到了数字8上面。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10328400" >
			<content effect_num="0" >不是7点就该响吗？搞什么飞机啊？</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10328500" >
			<content effect_num="0" >而且，为什么音姐明明知道我快迟到了，也没叫我起床？</content>			
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10328600" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1">完了，全勤奖学金没了。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2">就算现在把火箭绑在腿上，也赶不上早读的时间。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10328700" >
			<content effect_num="0" >算了，既然这样就慢慢来吧。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10328800" >
			<content effect_num="0" >音姐不在。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10328900" >
			<content effect_num="0" >已经冷下来的早点放在桌上，旁边还有一张字条。</content>			
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10329000" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1">“抱歉，刚刚接到公司的通知，需要马上赶去，所以不能一起吃早餐了。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2">我把你的那一份做好了，吃的话请先热一热。”</content>																					
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10329100" >
			<content effect_num="0" >“因为看你睡得很香，所以没有叫醒你。希望你不要因此而迟到。”</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10329200" >
			<content effect_num="0" >――已经迟到了啊，音姐。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10329300" >
			<content effect_num="0" >我无奈地叹息着。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10329400" >
			<content effect_num="0" >对我来说最惋惜的不是从掌心飞走的全勤奖学金，而是没能像往常那样在早晨看到她的笑容。</content>				
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10329500" >
			<content effect_num="0" >以往，这笑容是让我一天都充满动力的精神粮食。</content>			
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10329600" next_p="10329602">
			<content effect_num="0" >而且，本来盘算着和她解释卢医生的事情，这个计划也只好泡汤了。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10329602" next_p="10330300">
			<content effect_num="0" >抱着不快的情绪，我独自一人默默吃起了早餐。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10330300" end_scence_sound="true">
			<content effect_num="2" >到学校时已经是9点钟，第二堂课的时间。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10330400" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1">众目睽睽之下，我厚着脸皮走进了教室。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2">对于我的迟到，连老师也很吃惊。在和她对视时，我发现那张满是鱼尾纹的脸变成了“濉弊中汀_</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10330500" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="教师">李俊明同学，鉴于这是你第一次旷课，我就不追究了。希望你以后不要再犯。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10330600" >
			<content effect_num="0" >我有什么办法？谁叫闹钟报时莫名其妙变成了8点。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10330700" >
			<content effect_num="0" >不过，说起来，难道闹钟被谁做了手脚吗？</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10330800" >
			<content effect_num="0" >家里就我和音姐两人，而她绝不可能做这种类似恶作剧的事情。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10330900" >
			<content effect_num="0" >难道我潜意识里对该死的闹钟存有对抗情绪，于是在无意识的状态下调整了它的时间？</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10331000" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1">……算了，这种事情没有考虑的必要。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2">既然后果已经酿成，那么回家之后把它修正回来就是了。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10331100" >
			<content effect_num="0" >现在要考虑的，是出门忘记带午饭的我，怎么解决临近中午时肚子的抗议。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10331200" >
			<content effect_num="0" >不对，不是临近。现在已经是中午了。</content>			
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10331300" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1">翻遍了身上的兜，也只找到一个五毛钱的硬币。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2">――连买面包都不够。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10331400" start_scence_sound="950002.mp3">
			<content effect_num="0" talker="？？？">哦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦――！</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10331500" next_p="10331502">
			<content effect_num="0" >有危险！</content>	
	</para_msg>
  <para_msg paragraph="10331502" isselect="true">
			<content effect_num="0" />
			<select_label select_type="10012" start_select_paragrapha="10331700">A.朝左边闪</select_label>
			<select_label select_type="10013" start_select_paragrapha="10332300">B.朝右边闪</select_label>																				
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10331700" select_type="10012">
			<content effect_num="0" >我可不愿被同一伎俩KO两次。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10331800" select_type="10012">
			<content effect_num="0" >身体已经先做出了判断，朝座位左边一闪。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10331900" select_type="10012">
			<content effect_num="0" >然后，那只红色的野猫就从我刚才坐的地方飞了过去。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10332000" select_type="10012">
			<content effect_num="0" index="1">――这疯子，竟然是直接跃起，一个飞腿踹过来的。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2">她根本就是要杀人……</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10332100" select_type="10012">
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢兰">哎呀，真可惜。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10332200" select_type="10012" next_p="10335900">
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">你能不能改变一下自己的登场方式？！</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10332300" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="0" index="1">这样的叫声，只可能是那个疯丫头了。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2">――真是个永远都学不好的问题儿童。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10332400" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="0" >当然，我一万个不情愿在这家伙身上吃亏。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10332500" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="0" >在她的喊叫迫近的同时，我已经向右边挪动了一下身子。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10332600" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢兰">啊咧？啊咧咧咧咧咧咧咧咧――？！</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10332700" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢兰">哇！</content>																	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10332800" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="0" >红色的野猫从我刚才坐着的地方飞过去，活像失控的模型飞机。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10332900" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="0" index="1">――不对，也许形容成被醉酒的驾驶员操纵的卡车更加合适。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2">因为她这一飞直接撞倒了整整一个竖排的桌椅，如同制造车祸现场。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10333000" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="3" effect_type="timerStop">最后，她一头栽进自己制造的垃圾堆里――以屁股朝天的姿势。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10333100" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="1" >真是火辣的镜头啊，疯丫头。整个教室的人都看见了你裙下的纯白色哦。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10333200" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="1" talker="卢兰">呜……痛……</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10333300" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="0" >她花了不少时间才总算挣扎起身，然后朝我这边走过来。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10333400" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢兰">看见了吧？</content>								
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10333500" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">嗯，看见了。白色的，隐约能瞅到一个猫吃玉米的图案。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10333600" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢兰">那就好……</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10333700" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="0" index="1">她竟然还笑得出来。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2">不过，冲我伸出手是什么意思？</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10333800" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢兰">一百块，一口价。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10333900" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">哈？</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10334000" select_type="10013">
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢兰">参观费。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10334100" select_type="10013" next_p="10335900">
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">……如果我说“不”呢？</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10335900" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢兰">哎哟，好强硬的口气。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10336000" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" talker="卢兰">和我这样顶嘴的话，真的好么？</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" talker="卢兰">这份便当――我可就不给你了哦？</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10336100" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">便当？什么便当？</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10336200" >
			<content effect_num="0" >在我提出疑问的同时，卢兰像是变戏法一样，掌心忽然出现了一个用红色的口袋包着的饭盒。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10336300" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢兰">喏，就是这个。给你的。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10336400" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢兰">猜猜是谁做的？我们的万人迷学长。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10336500" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">…… ……</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10336600" >
			<content effect_num="0" >不会吧？难道……</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10336700" >
			<content effect_num="0" >这时候，我发现教室里所有的人都把目光集中到了我身上。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10336800" >
			<content effect_num="0" >所谓“如芒在背”，大概就是对我现在感觉的最贴切描述吧？</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10336900" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" >我脑子里产生了一个非常大胆也非常恐怖的猜测。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" >我想也许其他人里也有和我抱着同样想法的人。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10337000" >
			<content effect_num="0" >万一猜中的话……我很难想象会发生什么事。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10337100" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="？？？">啊，卢同学，等……等一下！</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10337200" >
			<content effect_num="0" >刚才的……是幻听吧？</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10337300" >
			<content effect_num="0" >一定是幻听。我实际上什么都没听见，什么都不知道。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10337400" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" >可惜，我不能像驼鸟那样把脑袋埋在沙子里然后宣称全世界与我无关。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" >该面对的现实还是不得不去面对的。</content>			
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10337500" >
			<content effect_num="0" >因为，从教室的前后门方向，更多的视线投了过来。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10337600" >
			<content effect_num="0" >――好像，全年级的男性都出动了。</content>			
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10337700" >
			<content effect_num="0" >接下来会发生什么事情，似乎是顺理成章的。</content>			
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10337800" >
			<content effect_num="0" >抱歉了啊，李俊明同学，你刚才没有出现幻听。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10337900" >
			<content effect_num="0" >在众人的拥簇下，那位小小的、可爱的公主隆重登场了。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10338000" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">卢同学！那个……那个……</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10338100" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢兰">呐，我已经帮你说了哦，谭佳。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10338200" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢兰">为了向某笨蛋表示你对他昨天一整天没来学校的担忧，你辛辛苦苦做了便当送给他。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10338300" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢兰">王子和公主从此过上了幸福的日子。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10338400" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">诶诶诶――！</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10338500" >
			<content effect_num="0" >这……也太乱来了吧？</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10338600" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" >谭佳的脸红得像大番茄一样。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" >我怀疑现在把生鸡蛋放在她头上，两秒钟就能烤熟。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10338700" >
			<content effect_num="0" >疯丫头做得过火了。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10338800" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">好了，疯丫头！别为难谭佳……同学。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10338900" >
			<content effect_num="0" >我是在众人敌视的目光下补充完最后两个字的。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10339000" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢兰">我可没有为难她哦，只是帮她把真心话说出来而已。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10339100" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢兰">好啦，便当已经送到。王子大人是不是该有点什么表示呢？</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10339200" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">表示？这……</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10339300" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">啊，学长，请不要太在意卢同学的话！</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10339400" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">实际上只是今天早上便当做得太多了！而且前天的事情真的很抱歉，所以想送一点吃的给您……</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10339500" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">那个，我听说在同龄人之间赠送礼物的话，食物是最受欢迎的！</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10339600" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢兰">唉，谭佳啊，你就是这样拐弯抹角的，事情进展才一直不顺。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10339700" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">蕖_</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10339800" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" talker="卢兰">好啦，总之事情就是这样。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" talker="卢兰">姓李的，你自己选吧。是老老实实陪谭佳同学吃一顿美好的午饭呢，还是留在教室里然后被这么多男生揉成麻花？</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10339900" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">呃……</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10340000" >
			<content effect_num="0" >她不说的话我还差点忘了，我现在正处于将要被男同胞们围攻的状态。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10340100" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" >事情闹得稍微有点大，整个教室都喧哗起来。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" >要是被哪个路过的老师看见这情景的话，我就算有一百张嘴都解释不清楚。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10340200" >
			<content effect_num="0" >在被群殴之前，走为上策。再说肚子也的确饿得慌。</content>		
