			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">蕖…就是您和卢同学是怎么认识的_</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10351000" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">对刚才卢同学说的那些话，我有那么一点在意。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10351100" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">…… ……</content>					
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10351200" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" >居然问这个……这可是我非常不想提起的事。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" >不过，谭佳似乎很想知道。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10351300" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">你确定你想听？告诉你的话也无所谓。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10351400" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" talker="谭佳">嗯，我想知道。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" talker="谭佳">我们是朋友吧？</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10351500" >
			<content effect_num="0">朋友……么？</content>			
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10351600" >
			<content effect_num="0">被漂亮的女生主动这样说，我却未觉得很高兴。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10351700" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" >我有认真地把她当作朋友么？</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" >――我这样问自己，但不知如何回答。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10351800" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" >不过，这也不是什么坏事。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" >看着她那真诚的样子，我难以狠下心否认她说的话。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10351900" >
			<content effect_num="0">朋友啊――和这样的女孩子做朋友，不管从什么角度说都不算是坏事。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10352000" >
			<content effect_num="0">姑且就这样承认好了。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10352100" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">那好吧，我先梳理一下头绪……</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10352200" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">事情得从这学期第一天说起。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10352300" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">当时我因为需要办理一些手续，所以第一堂课都快结束了才赶往教室。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10352400" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" talker="李俊明">正好，有个女生和我一样因为办手续的问题而晚到了。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" talker="李俊明">那个家伙就是卢兰。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10352500" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">我在楼道上撞见她。她长得很不错，脸上一直挂着笑容。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10352600" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">虽然我们都没说话，但是在安静的走廊上并肩行走的感觉挺不错。</content>																																							
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10352700" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">但很快，灾难就发生了。</content>																		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10352800" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" talker="李俊明">似乎是高一（3）班的人干的好事。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" talker="李俊明">我也不知道他们玩的是什么把戏，反正当时我就看到他们几乎全班出动，如同土匪一样从走廊上奔过。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10352900" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">他们当时把一个中年男人举过头顶，一帮人抬着他，像是要去搞什么游行。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10353000" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" talker="李俊明">我正好在走廊转角的地方撞见他们，连躲闪都来不及。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" talker="李俊明">这些亢奋的家伙简直像是要把我直接踩扁一样，轰轰烈烈地就那样冲过去了。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10353100" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">我被他们狠狠撞了一下，晕头转向。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10353200" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" talker="李俊明">回过神来的时候，我发现那帮人已经走远。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" talker="李俊明">而我趴在地上。卢兰就站在我旁边。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10353300" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">…… ……</content>												
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10353400" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">之后呢？</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10353500" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">我被撞倒的时候，一只手不小心拽到了她的裙子。</content>																																																																																																							
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10353600" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">我竟然就这样把她的裙子给整个儿拉下来了……</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10353700" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">吓？！</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10353800" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">我真不是故意的！</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10353900" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">但是，我正准备道歉的时候，她抓住了我的手，然后竟然把手掌放在她的大腿上！</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10354000" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">蓿『孟窈茉愀饽亍_</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10354100" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">你知道她当时说了什么吗？</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10354200" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">我模仿一下――</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10354300" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">“这位同学，现在走廊上只有我们两个人吧？”</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10354400" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">“然后呢，你拽下了我的裙子，一只咸猪手还在我身上摸来摸去。”</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10354500" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">“如果我这时候大声尖叫‘非礼啊！’的话，会发生什么有趣的事情呢？”</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10354600" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">我一辈子都忘不了她说那句话时，脸上的表情。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10354700" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">我被抓住把柄了……不过，也多亏那样，我深刻了解了这丫头的性格有多差劲。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10354800" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">喏，事情经过就是这样。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10354900" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">_Q……</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10355000" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">Q？</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10355100" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" talker="谭佳">哈哈……哈哈！原来学长和卢同学是这样认识的！</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" talker="谭佳">哈哈……我不行了……抱歉，但是……哈哈……</content>																									
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10355200" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">真的忍不住了……呵呵――哈哈――！</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10355300" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" >这下子，她笑得比刚才更加夸张。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" >完全抛弃了之前小鸟依人的作风，像天真的孩子一样快乐地笑着。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10355400" >
			<content effect_num="0">看到她这样，似乎没必要再多说什么了……</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10355500" >
			<content effect_num="0">大概是因为谭佳的确很可爱，笑容也没有恶意的缘故，我并不讨厌她因为我以前的尴尬经历而发笑。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10355600" >
			<content effect_num="0">――真是个不管做什么都无法让人对她生起气来的人。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10355700" next_p="10360200">
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" >我无奈地冲她耸肩，打开了她送给我的饭盒。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" >姑且把她的笑声当作下饭菜吧。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10360200" >
			<content effect_num="2" sound="960014.mp3" talker="谭佳">时间过得很快呢。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10360300" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">唔……嗯……的确呢……</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10360400" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">蓿抗然和我一起吃饭会很无聊吧_</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10360500" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">不，我不是这个意思。</content>										
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10360600" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">如果和你待在一起也会无聊的话，恐怕世上就没有什么有趣事了。</content>			
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10360700" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">我倒是希望和你在一起的时间能持续得更久一些。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10360800" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">吓？</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10360900" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" >话刚脱口我就后悔了。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" >在这种场合下，对谭佳说这样的话，似乎有些失礼。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10361000" >
			<content effect_num="0">不论从怎样的角度去看，这都类似于告白的用语。但实际上我并未产生告白的念头。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10361100" >
			<content effect_num="0" >只是和字面意思一样的单纯意义而已――我喜欢的是像今天午饭时这种气氛。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10361200" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" >和谭佳在一起，总会令我有一种“被治愈了”的安心感。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" >这种感觉，以前走出家门就不曾体会过。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10361300" >
			<content effect_num="0" >既然她把我当成朋友，那我也十分乐意与她做朋友。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10361400" >
			<content effect_num="0" >但是，把心里话通过嘴巴实际表达出来，却似乎会造成相反的效果。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10361500" >
			<content effect_num="0" >谭佳现在的表情就在告诉我，她会错了意。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10361600" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">啊，我的意思是……</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10361700" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">蓿那个…_</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10361800" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">学长，您是个很好的人，但是……</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10361900" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="谭佳">抱……抱歉！</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10362000" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" >好像……连解释的余地都没给我留。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" >她红着脸跑了，只留下一句道歉语，还有愣在原地的我。</content>																									
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10362100" next_p="10362300">
			<content effect_num="0" >这下子误会大了……</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10362300" end_scence_sound="true">
			<content effect_num="2" >整个下午，我都在思考怎样和谭佳解释。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10362400" >
			<content effect_num="0" >太鲁莽了，说话不动脑子――这是我对自己的评价。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10362500" >
			<content effect_num="0" >本来很好的气氛，因为我一句是是而非的话，导致了双方的尴尬。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10362600" >
			<content effect_num="0" >谭佳是个很纤细的女孩子，这种突兀的告白――虽然我本意绝非那样――定然会造成她的莫大困扰。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10362700" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" >必须和她解释清楚。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" >我虽然很喜欢她，但并不是作为男性爱慕女性的那种喜欢。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10362800" >
			<content effect_num="2" >但是，放学后，谭佳并未像前两天那样出现。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10362900" >
			<content effect_num="0" >也难怪，出于好心给我做了便当，却突然收到那样突兀的“告白”，性格内向的她当然会受不了。</content>															
  </para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10363000" >
			<content effect_num="0" >但我还是想当面和她解释清楚。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10363100" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" >算了，看这样子只好等明天再说。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" >我叹了口气，动手收拾书包。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10363200" next_p="10363202" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" >话说回来，今天的学校好安静。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" >社团活动似乎比以往结束得还要早，而且大家都像得到了什么指令一样离去了。</content>					
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10363202" next_p="10363204">
			<content effect_num="0" index="1" >从教室的窗户朝操场上看，别说人影了，连只猫都没有。</content>
			<content effect_num="0" index="2" >真是奇怪，明明放学钟声响起之后才过了5分钟……</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10363204" next_p="10373500">
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">喂喂……大家都被某个魔术师催眠了么？</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10373500" >
			<content effect_num="0" >我故意大声调侃道，但马上就想起就算叫得再大声估计也没人听见。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10373600" >
			<content effect_num="0" >真没意思……突然觉得自己就像个傻瓜一样。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10373700" >
			<content effect_num="0" >既然这样，那我也回去吧……</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10373800" >
			<content effect_num="1" talker="李俊明">――――――――――！</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10373900" start_scence_sound="950003.mp3">
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">呜――――！</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10374000" >
			<content effect_num="0" >猝不及防的，极端的不谐感如电流般贯穿身心。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10374100" >
			<content effect_num="1" >仅仅是一瞬间的感知，就觉得从皮肉到骨头都像是分崩离析了一般。</content>							
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10374200" >
			<content effect_num="0" >好难受――脑子里不停地重复着唯一的念头。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10374300" >
			<content effect_num="0" >非常难受……痛苦得恨不得立刻就这样死了好。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10374400" >
			<content effect_num="1" talker="李俊明">啊――啊啊啊！！</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10374500" >
			<content effect_num="0" >从小腿开始，肌肉发生了痉挛。</content>			
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10374600" >
			<content effect_num="0" >我跪倒在地，身子蜷成一团，但这无法让痛楚有丝毫减弱。</content>				
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10374700" >
			<content effect_num="0" >视野模糊起来，脑海里渐渐变得一片空白。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10374800" next_p="10375000">
			<content effect_num="0" >好痛……而且……好累……</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10375000" >
			<content effect_num="2" >像被钢针刺中心脏一样。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10375100" >
			<content effect_num="0" >像被铁锤反复敲打头颅一样。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10375200" >
			<content effect_num="0" >被阵痛折磨得晕过去，然后又因痛楚而惊醒――我已不记得自己经历了多少次这样的循环。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10375300" >
			<content effect_num="0" >从来没有担心过生死的我，现在竟开始害怕起来。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10375400" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1">在这个没有人的教室里，反复地遭受折磨。</content>							
			<content effect_num="0" index="2">无人知晓，更不会有人伸出援手。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10375500" >
			<content effect_num="0" >我……会不会就这样死掉？</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10375600" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1">不会吧……绝对不会。</content>							
			<content effect_num="0" index="2">健康的高中生在放学后暴毙，这不管怎么看都像是黑色喜剧里才会发生的事。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10375700" >
			<content effect_num="0" >但是，为什么会这么害怕呢？明明应该先搞明白为何会突然被阵痛侵袭才对吧？</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10375800" >
			<content effect_num="0" >强忍着痛，我勉强扭转僵硬的脖子，朝窗外望去。</content>							
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10375900" >
			<content effect_num="0" >夕阳还是悬挂在老地方。连时间都像是为了看我的笑话而故意停了下来一样。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10376000" >
			<content effect_num="0" >快来个人吧――我害怕地祈祷。快点，来个人发现我，帮我一把……</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10376100" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="？？？">哟，竟然用这么夸张的姿势趴着，你是在思考爬行动物的进化史么？</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10376200" >
			<content effect_num="0" >突如其来的问询。</content>											
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10376300" >
			<content effect_num="0" >一如既往的戏谑口气，似乎还包含了点嘲弄的意味在里面。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10376400" >
			<content effect_num="0" >虽然没有力气抬起头看说话的人，但听声音就能轻易猜出是谁。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10376500" >
			<content effect_num="0" >她是什么时候来的？明明连脚步声都没听到。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10376600" >
			<content effect_num="0" >简直就像是幽灵一样，突然就出现在我身边。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10376700" >
			<content effect_num="0" >在我百思不得其解时，她已经伸出双臂，将我扶了起来。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10376800" >
			<content effect_num="0" >我有气无力地坐在椅子上，而她就站在我面前。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10376900" >
			<content effect_num="0" >虽然脑子里还是嗡嗡作响，但残存的意识依然在告诉我，这个女人和我之间的距离很暧昧。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10377000" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1">――她似乎故意贴近我。</content>							
			<content effect_num="0" index="2">在安静的夕阳之下，我不仅能清晰地看见她丰满胸脯的一起一伏，甚至能听清她细若蚊蚋的喘息声。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10377100" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢缘">你比我想象中要轻很多，但还是比小猫小狗什么的重一些。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10377200" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢缘">话说，被一个成熟的美女搀扶起来，你就不能有点绅士风度么？至少也该对我说声“谢谢”什么的。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10377300" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">…… ……</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10377400" >
			<content effect_num="0" >我的确很想道谢，但现在连吐一个字的力气都没有。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10377500" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢缘">…… ……</content>							
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10377600" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢缘">唔……不过，你似乎也没必要道谢。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10377700" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢缘">因为我接下来想对你做的事情，无论怎么看也不可能让你产生道谢的念头。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10377800" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="李俊明">…… ……</content>			
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10377900" >
			<content effect_num="0" >她这番话是什么意思？我没听明白。</content>						
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10378000" next_p="10378200">
			<content effect_num="0" >她想对我做什么？</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10378200" >
			<content effect_num="1" sound="960027.mp3">――――――――！</content>			
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10378300" >
			<content effect_num="0" >这……这是怎么回事？</content>			
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10378400" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1">我吃惊地把手伸向捂住了胸口。</content>	
			<content effect_num="0" index="2">冰冷的、锋利的金属物，分毫不差地穿过了肋骨的空隙，深深扎入其下的脆弱器官。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10378500" >
			<content effect_num="0" >我不明白，一点都不明白。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10378600" >
			<content effect_num="0" >大脑拒绝思考，只有透彻骨髓的痛为我道出真相。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10378700" next_p="10378702">
			<content effect_num="0" >渐渐失去力气的手，放在痛楚的中心处，我心脏的位置。</content>	
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10378702" next_p="10378800">
			<content effect_num="0" />
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10378800" >
			<content effect_num="0" >手心是湿漉漉的一片。温热的液体向身子外涌动着，穿过指缝，无可挽回地流逝。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10378900" >
			<content effect_num="0" >好冷――除了掌心之外，全身上下没有一处不觉得冷。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10379000" >
			<content effect_num="0" >我……还是不明白。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10379100" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢缘">很痛么？但请你忍耐并且接受吧，这是没有办法的办法。</content>			
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10379200" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢缘">原谅我……原谅我在此时此刻杀掉了你……</content>				
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10379300" >
			<content effect_num="0" talker="卢缘">――――</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10379400" >
			<content effect_num="0" >她口中还在念叨着，但我已听不清了。</content>				
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10379500" >
			<content effect_num="0" index="1">似乎，她是在呼唤谁的名字。</content>							
			<content effect_num="0" index="2">一个对我来说很陌生，但又像是有那么一点印象的名字。</content>				
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10379600" >
			<content effect_num="2" index="1">可是，无法再思考她话中的深意了。</content>	
			<content effect_num="0" index="2">甚至连质问她“为什么要刺我”都做不到……什么都，做不到。</content>
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10379700" >
			<content effect_num="0" >鲜血带着生命力离去。我整个人就像掉入了黑色的深渊里一样。从身体到灵魂，渐渐地被无尽的黑暗浸染。</content>		
	</para_msg>
	<para_msg paragraph="10379800" next_p="10379802">
			<content effect_num="0" >――直到最后，再也无法感觉到任何东西为止。</content>
	</para_msg>
